{"id":"2023-japan-07","collection":"2023-japan","date":"2023 February 16","title":"Hakuba - Iwatake","content":"Today was snowboarding at Iwatake.\n\nI remembered this mountain from my first trip to Hakuba 9 years earlier - the single gondola to the \"peak\" / middle of the mountain gives access to runs all over the mountain, then the chairlifts bring you back to the central hub again.\n\nThe weather was pretty spectacular most of the day, and this made for a very fun day of boarding. The runs are nice and wide, and the mountain just has a fun feel to it compared to others which can be a bit busy or rushed feeling. I spent most of the morning hanging around the shorter runs, then after lunch did a few of the full runs back to the base of the mountain. It was a lot of fun again!","images":[{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1wZyt5qX2UD4eS0RmrHZG3inm5ETsGcX8?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/187llgjatWJr5xAS3HzP1dVr-QkIT9ici?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1B6KzFj4n6q-r93PTSBWH9ef5H9Dnuql-?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1ROMHCo4AzV0saeDWGhqk535MHpFNsp8z?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1I1A8_TA6ogToeUL_lExJ0KzuHKBgkv5B?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1Eea1t9e0d1Y4ua3MfDDgm-vatdyxaE6v?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1CsMLuzCq93sX6n_4sOaGOnSaMintlAeB?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/14Jil8AWVjdmddqAlDKhFteJToh2cm_Vz?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1SmD2ZbfBzUZL04Xvv43-Clvwfc85S8-c?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1OXjG1Wr-pS3vM6N0MA2TX4aHAVgnXPBG?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1677L7w-jZQODMcLiJw5-oUjAnjXAIi8c?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1lP76gfBHSkSf1779RSHH2Iyil8HmYY0b?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1Ca1g4SnxwHeuVhfmR80tia3dq_WeFkXZ?authus